01.06.02 Release CLHEP-1.8.0.0
==============================


Fri May 24 14:44:32 2002 Mark Fischler <mf@fnal.gov>

	* Vector/Rotation.cc,RotationA.cc,RotationE.cc,RotationX.cc:
